    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Armbands worn on the upper arm, usually made of gold, but also made from a range of other materials (wood, leather, etc.) in postclassic central Mexico.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
