            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ce coztli tlen yohui pan ahcolli, maz tepoztli tlen teocuitlatl zanpampa nouhquiya ica cequinoc tlamantli (huapalli, cuetlaxtli, etc.) pan Mexco central posclásico.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
